{"tid":805593,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Snapdragon 8180 處理器現身 為高階 Windows 10 筆電而設","createTime":"2018-09-04T03:03:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T09:40:50.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"33608727e5c5920057c4f590ecf56a844f28a276","tid":805593,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:03:10.000Z","msg":"唐美鳳<br />\n<br />\n現時的電腦處理器種類比以往多，原本主力生產平板等流動裝置處理器的 Qualcomm，其 Snapdragon 系列處理器亦開始應用於 Windows 10 筆電。去年公佈使用 Snapdragon 835 處理器的筆電，今年陸續上市，早前 Lenovo 亦表示使用 Snapdragon 850 處理器的筆電會在年底前發售。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n日前在跑分網站 Geekbench 的數據庫中，就出現了一款全新的 Qualcomm 處理器的跑分成績，似乎這晶片生產商正秘密開發專為 Windows 10 高階筆電而設的處理器。這款在 GeekBench 4 出現的處理器型號為 Snapdragon 8180，使用新的 ARM Cortex A76 內核，測試的裝置搭配 8GB RAM 和 32-bit 的 Windows 10 系統，單核跑分為 1,392，而多核得分則有 4,286 分。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\nSnapdragon 835 和 850 處理器只是 Qualcomm 的第一步，Snapdragon 8180 才是讓他們真正邁向筆電處理器生產商，挑戰其他傳統電腦處理器生產商的重要棋子。"},{"pid":"497570be609874d5c8a29f321b8c6c573b1f64a9","tid":805593,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T03:03:50.000Z","msg":"大家點睇ARM版notebook???有無機會取代到x86嘅notebook??<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/804789\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/804789</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3fe9b538de0dd579187746bf5bbf8edbd83265b9","tid":805593,"uid":28563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"仲以為xeon platinum 8180，好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfec6a1085ff88001b9db063cdba3dc365638808","tid":805593,"uid":28563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3fe9b538de0dd579187746bf5bbf8edbd83265b9","tid":805593,"uid":28563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:44:00.000Z","msg":"仲以為xeon platinum 8180，好失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:45:22.000Z","msg":"望到高階，望到8180，真心